Title: Invicta Men's 1251 Pro-Diver Chronograph Silver Dial Watch
Description: Item: Invicta Men's 1251 Pro-Diver Chronograph Silver Dial Watch Description: This Limited Edition creation represents the first ever Invicta timepiece showing the stamped signature of Invicta President & CEO, Eyal Lalo. This Limited Edition Pro Diver from Invicta makes a stylish splash with a 45mm round case executed in cutting edge silver-tone tungsten. A unidirectional rotating ceramic bezel with a scalloped edge and raised polished silver-tone diver's scale surrounds the protective Flame Fusion crystal. The stainless steel Limited Edition numbered case back proudly shows the stamped signature of Invicta President & CEO, Eyal Lalo. A round sunray dial in silver-tone displays metallic trimmed luminous Tritnite Arabic numerals at all hour positions except 3:00 and 9:00. A date window appears near 3:00 along with the Invicta name. Second, hour and minute subdials exist near 6:00, 9:00 and 12:00, respectively. A Japanese TMI VK67 Quartz Chronograph movement drives the Tritnite accented hour, minute and chronograph hands along with subdial hands. Tungsten outer links combine with highly scratch resistant bezel coordinating ceramic center links in blue to construct the 22mm wide bracelet. A deployment clasp decorated with the Invicta name and logo secures the watch to your wrist.
